      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COOL IT MISTER (2) missed the frame last time out when sixth at this track from Box four (20.64) but draws same box here as latest win. Form here at the trip sound including seven wins. Speedy beginner who should be prominent early on from an inside box. Has ability and looks hard to stop. ASTON HANSON (4) was checked in the run and safely held when sixth (21.42) in a Other over 342m at this track. Solid beginner and with a good start can clear the tricky draw. Better than latest and worth another try. ANTECEDENT (7) comes off an average run last start when sixth at this track over 342m behind Smooth Paradise (20.58) in a Other. Strong form has emerged from her last run. Has ability and can measure up. BELLA MAPLE (8) placed at long odds last time and cannot be ignored.",
